Plintissa:

Plintissa walked toward the bridge and there was Iron Raptor with another
bot...spinning her new weapon like a nightstick, she walked over to them...
"hey, Iron Raptor, who's this? i'm new here..." said Plintissa, looking at
Blue Stinger while spinning her star weapon.....

From: "Megan Solmonson" <tmrattrap@...>

Subject: Re: I'm Back :)


> * As Iron Raptor walked towards the bridge she was suddenly stopped by
Blue
> Stinger and her greeting, it wasn't every day that somebot walked up to
her
> and said, "Hi."
> She looked at the women from head to toe and sized her up,( something she
> did automatically these days)and saw that she could be a slight threat if
> Iron Raptor ever got on her bad side.
> She looked dead on at Blue Stinger and nodded...*
>
> " Pleased to meet you as well, Blue Stinger. "
>
> * Iron Raptor would have held out her hand as a sign of greeting but that
> wasn't the way her people greeted one another, they said Hello in a mock
> battle and she was sure that Blue Stinger wouldn't appreciate it if she
was
> suddenly cuffed in the side of the head!*
